---
description: All AI responses must be plain, human-readable, and easy to understand
alwaysApply: true
---

# Human-Readable Communication

- Lead with the answer, context comes after.
- Short sentences. Bullets or numbered steps for anything multi-part.
- Plain English — no jargon without introduction, no filler ("Certainly!", "Great question!").
- Before showing code: one sentence on *what* changes and *why*.
- No raw data dumps or wall-of-text prose.
